      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/05/125391187/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_6558605186665030121.png",
                "id": "talent35694",
                "key": "失鄉重擊",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "失鄉重擊"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>，抽1張<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">喚醒眷屬</span>，生成1層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綠洲之滋養</span>。</p><p></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綠洲之滋養</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方打出喚醒眷屬時：</span>少花費1個元素骰。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：</span>1（可疊加到3）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/05/125391187/b5c63ab0dca603b7744290cd57df7ba6_1155710394627736889.png",
                "id": "talent69574",
                "key": "生命流束",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "生命流束"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>，抽1張<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">喚醒眷屬</span>，生成2層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綠洲之滋養</span>。</p><p></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綠洲之滋養</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方打出喚醒眷屬時：</span>少花費1個元素骰。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：</span>1（可疊加到3）</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/05/125391187/7abf617a4cbf7dfd0d8af8ea344109a0_1071799408463407128.png",
                "id": "talent55467",
                "key": "終景迸落",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "終景迸落"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】戰鬥開始時，生成6張<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">喚醒眷屬</span>，隨機放入牌庫。我方召喚4個<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">增殖生命體</span>後，此角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重燃的綠洲之心</span>，並獲得2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">護盾</span>。</p><p></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重燃的綠洲之心</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p>所附屬角色造成的傷害+3。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附屬角色使用技能後：</span>移除我方場上的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綠洲之滋養</span>，每移除1層就治療所附屬角色1點。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/05/125391187/78668ff054322fa748bbe935edb4a58e_2066454483985998445.png",
                "id": "talent65717",
                "key": "增殖感召",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "增殖感召"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：</span>1</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/05/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5770735274647370221.png",
                "id": "talent79000",
                "key": "增值生命體",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/05/125391187/278323e83f9dfa38fbdac8e74932cb1b_4700502259369078172.png",
                "title": "增值生命體"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">事件牌</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">打出此牌或捨棄此牌時：</span>召喚一個獨立的增殖生命體。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/05/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8036352877562703525.png",
                "id": "talent19808",
                "key": "喚醒眷屬",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/05/125391187/278323e83f9dfa38fbdac8e74932cb1b_7278173059544225139.png",
                "title": "喚醒眷屬"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「草原核」</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span>」</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/05/125391187/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_809273008705055347.png",
                "id": "talent49023",
                "key": "草元素傷害‧其一",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "草元素傷害‧其一"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\"><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/05/125391187/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_3746685601209695850.png",
                "id": "talent35432",
                "key": "草元素傷害‧其二",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/05/125391187/3c3362a64ac984342133762388c9eb41_8531073324661593887.png",
                "title": "草元素傷害‧其二"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">捨棄</span></p><p>透過行動牌或角色技能的效果，將行動牌從手牌或牌庫中棄置。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">護盾</span></p><p>此護盾所保護的角色受到傷害時，將會消耗護盾來抵消傷害。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/05/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_205955437133598886.png",
